encoded.label: Encoded
encoded.description: Indicates whether any column in the table has compression encoding defined.

stats_off.label: Stats Off
stats_off.description: Number that indicates how stale the table statistics are; 0 is current, 100 is out of date.

diststyle.label: Dist Style
diststyle.description: Distribution style or distribution key column, if key distribution is defined.

rows.label: Approximate Row Count
rows.description: Approximate number of rows in the table. This value includes rows marked for deletion, but not yet vacuumed.

max_varchar.label: Max Varchar
max_varchar.description: Size of the largest column that uses a VARCHAR data type.

pct_used.label: Disk Utilization
pct_used.description: Percent of available space that is used by the table.

sortkey1.label: Sort Key 1
sortkey1.description: First column in the sort key.

size.label: Approximate Size
size.description: Approximate size of the table, calculated from a count of 1MB blocks
